[l] Oh, ach, auch Fluglinienpersonal wie Piloten und Flugbegleiter fallen unter das Trump-Einwanderungsverbot.Wer sich uebrigens fragt, wieso da irgendwelche muslimischen Laender in dem Dekret stehen: Rudi "9/11" Giuliani klaergt das mal auf.“I’ll tell you the whole history of it,” Giuliani said in an interview with Fox News’ Jeanine Pirro on Saturday night. “When he first announced it, he said ‘Muslim ban.’ He called me up. He said, ‘Put a commission together. Show me the right way to do it legally.'”
